{"tid":230767,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"蔡英文上台　陸客大減 旅業嚴冬","createTime":"2017-05-05T15:01:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T15:01:20.000Z","uid":83648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"87afe770c1b363dbebf6b19b6aebf7e9264b07ea","tid":230767,"uid":83648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:01:20.000Z","msg":"【英文上台　陸客大減】<br />\n【旅業嚴冬　仍有淡市奇葩】<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/671370149721723/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F671370149721723%2F&d=3wrM%2FJom4zLweqSprMIx0smDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=04a12e44\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/671370149721723/</a><br />\n<br />\n在台灣，民進黨的蔡英文上台快將一年，兩岸關係降溫，旅遊業首當其衝。<br />\n<br />\n訪台陸客持續下跌，相關的旅遊業界都叫苦連天，但亦有從業者堅持一貫風格，為保持山川美景的寧靜安逸，放棄陸客團這塊「肥豬肉」，成為淡市中的奇葩。<br />\n<br />\n＃有線新聞　＃台灣　＃民進黨　＃蔡英文　＃旅遊業　＃大陸客　有線中國組<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有線提漏左大陸客少左16%<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但整體旅客多左2.4%</span></span><br />\nsource: <a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-38918378\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-38918378&d=3wrM%2FJom4zLweqSprMIx0smDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=ed99ef46\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-38918378&h=65635cea\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-38918378</a>"}]}